UV (recommended)
  uv sync --extra dev          # create .venv + install deps (incl. pytest)
  uv run python main.py        # web app → http://127.0.0.1:8000
  uv run pytest                # tests
  uv run python src/utils/map_osm.py --path 402365 401129

  Lockfile: uv lock / uv sync --locked (after dependency changes)

Classic venv + pip
  python3 -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate && pip install -r requirements.txt && python main.py
